<plot>Letters Lost is about a boy named Andrew who falls in love for the first time. The object of his affection is a young girl who frequents a lake after school. Unable to speak to her due to his shyness, he resorts to writing letters. Unfortunately, he is not a very good writer either. Luckily, he stumbles upon his parent's old love letters which he uses for inspiration. The past and present collide in this modern coming of age film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?333821</url></doc>
